        "subject": "LU-3803 tests: remove previouw $tdir in sanity 161c",
        "message": "LU-3803 tests: remove previouw $tdir in sanity 161c\n\nThe test 161c is assume the $tdir will be in MDT0, but\nactually $tdir(161d) left by 161a and 161b will be on\nMDT1, which will make 161 fails, so delete $tdir before\ntesting 161c.\n\nSigned-off-by: Wang Di <di.wang@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Ib8f17c6fed4a912049e99f57137ac1fb5426e22e\n"
